        "trimStrings": [],
        "replaceString": "```\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n<title>Branch Selector</title>\n<style>\n* { box-sizing: border-box; }\nbody {\n  margin: 0;\n  padding: 14px;\n  font-family: inherit;\n  background: transparent;\n  font-size: 14px;\n}\n.panel {\n  background: #fafafa;\n  border-top: 2px solid #111;\n  border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;\n  padding: 14px 0 0;\n}\n.header {\n  font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;\n  font-size: 8px;\n  letter-spacing: 3px;\n  text-transform: uppercase;\n  color: #bbb;\n  margin-bottom: 10px;\n  padding: 0 18px;\n}\n.option-list {\n  list-style: none;\n  padding: 0;\n  margin: 0;\n}\n.option-item {\n  display: flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  justify-content: space-between;\n  padding: 9px 18px;\n  cursor: pointer;\n  border-left: 2px solid transparent;\n  transition: all .18s;\n  color: #555;\n  font-size: 13px;\n  line-height: 1.4;\n}\n.option-item:hover {\n  border-left-color: #ccc;\n  background: #f5f5f5;\n  color: #111;\n}\n.option-item.selected {\n  border-left-color: #111;\n  background: #f0f0f0;\n  color: #111;\n}\n.opt-arrow {\n  font-size: 11px;\n  color: #ccc;\n  opacity: 0;\n  transition: opacity .18s, transform .18s;\n  transform: translateX(-4px);\n  flex-shrink: 0;\n  margin-left: 10px;\n}\n.option-item:hover .opt-arrow,\n.option-item.selected .opt-arrow {\n  opacity: 1;\n  transform: translateX(0);\n  color: #999;\n}\n.display {\n  margin: 10px 18px 14px;\n  padding: 8px 12px;\n  border-left: 2px solid #e8e8e8;\n  font-size: 12px;\n  color: #aaa;\n  min-height: 18px;\n  font-style: italic;\n  transition: all .2s;\n}\n.display.active {\n  border-left-color: #111;\n  color: #444;\n  font-style: normal;\n}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n<div class=\"panel\">\n  <div class=\"header\">Branch Selection</div>\n  <ul class=\"option-list\">\n    <li class=\"option-item\" onclick=\"pick(this,'$1')\"><span>$1</span><span class=\"opt-arrow\">→</span></li>\n    <li class=\"option-item\" onclick=\"pick(this,'$2')\"><span>$2</span><span class=\"opt-arrow\">→</span></li>\n    <li class=\"option-item\" onclick=\"pick(this,'$3')\"><span>$3</span><span class=\"opt-arrow\">→</span></li>\n    <li class=\"option-item\" onclick=\"pick(this,'$4')\"><span>$4</span><span class=\"opt-arrow\">→</span></li>\n    <li class=\"option-item\" onclick=\"pick(this,'$5')\"><span>$5</span><span class=\"opt-arrow\">→</span></li>\n  </ul>\n  <div class=\"display\" id=\"display\">未选择</div>\n</div>\n<script>\nlet last = null;\nfunction pick(el, txt) {\n  last?.classList.remove('selected');\n  el.classList.add('selected');\n  last = el;\n  const d = document.getElementById('display');\n  d.innerText = txt;\n  d.classList.add('active');\n  try {\n    const ta = window.parent.document.querySelector('#send_textarea');\n    if (!ta) return;\n    ta.value = txt;\n    ta.dispatchEvent(new Event('input', { bubbles: true }));\n  } catch(e) {}\n}\n</script>\n</body>\n</html>\n```",
