        "replaceString": "```\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n<title>Branch Selector</title>\n<style>\n* { box-sizing: border-box; }\nbody {\n  margin: 0;\n  padding: 14px;\n  font-family: inherit;\n  background: transparent;\n  font-size: 14px;\n}\n.panel {\n  background: linear-gradient(160deg, #fff8fc, #fef2fa);\n  border: 2px solid #f0c0dc;\n  border-radius: 20px;\n  overflow: hidden;\n  box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(240,150,190,.15);\n}\n.header {\n  background: linear-gradient(90deg, #fde4f2, #fdf0fa, #fde4f2);\n  padding: 11px 16px;\n  text-align: center;\n  font-size: 12px;\n  font-weight: 600;\n  color: #c05880;\n  letter-spacing: 3px;\n  border-bottom: 1.5px dashed #f4c0dc;\n  display: flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  justify-content: center;\n  gap: 10px;\n}\n.header-star {\n  color: #e8a0c0;\n  display: inline-block;\n  animation: spin 4s linear infinite;\n  font-size: 13px;\n}\n@keyframes spin { from { transform: rotate(0) } to { transform: rotate(360deg) } }\n.option-list {\n  list-style: none;\n  padding: 10px 12px;\n  margin: 0;\n  display: flex;\n  flex-direction: column;\n  gap: 7px;\n}\n.option-item {\n  display: flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  gap: 11px;\n  padding: 9px 13px;\n  border-radius: 12px;\n  cursor: pointer;\n  border: 1.5px solid transparent;\n  transition: all .2s cubic-bezier(.34,1.56,.64,1);\n  color: #7a3858;\n  background: rgba(255,255,255,.6);\n  font-size: 13px;\n  line-height: 1.4;\n}\n.option-item:hover {\n  border-color: #f0b0d0;\n  background: #fff0f8;\n  transform: scale(1.02);\n}\n.option-item.selected {\n  border-color: #e880b8;\n  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff0f8, #ffe8f4);\n  box-shadow: 0 3px 12px rgba(240,130,180,.2);\n}\n.opt-badge {\n  width: 22px;\n  height: 22px;\n  border-radius: 50%;\n  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f4c0dc, #e890c0);\n  color: #fff;\n  font-size: 10px;\n  font-weight: 700;\n  display: flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  justify-content: center;\n  flex-shrink: 0;\n  transition: transform .2s;\n}\n.option-item.selected .opt-badge {\n  transform: scale(1.15);\n  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e870b0, #d04090);\n}\n.display {\n  margin: 0 14px 14px;\n  padding: 10px 14px;\n  background: rgba(255,220,240,.3);\n  border-radius: 12px;\n  border: 1px solid rgba(240,160,200,.4);\n  font-size: 12px;\n  color: #c090a8;\n  text-align: center;\n  min-height: 18px;\n  font-style: italic;\n  transition: all .25s;\n}\n.display.active {\n  font-style: normal;\n  color: #903060;\n  background: rgba(255,200,230,.4);\n}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n<div class=\"panel\">\n  <div class=\"header\">\n    <span class=\"header-star\">✦</span>\n    选择你的故事\n    <span class=\"header-star\" style=\"animation-direction:reverse\">✦</span>\n  </div>\n  <ul class=\"option-list\">\n    <li class=\"option-item\" onclick=\"pick(this,'$1')\"><span class=\"opt-badge\">A</span><span>$1</span></li>\n    <li class=\"option-item\" onclick=\"pick(this,'$2')\"><span class=\"opt-badge\">B</span><span>$2</span></li>\n    <li class=\"option-item\" onclick=\"pick(this,'$3')\"><span class=\"opt-badge\">C</span><span>$3</span></li>\n    <li class=\"option-item\" onclick=\"pick(this,'$4')\"><span class=\"opt-badge\">D</span><span>$4</span></li>\n    <li class=\"option-item\" onclick=\"pick(this,'$5')\"><span class=\"opt-badge\">E</span><span>$5</span></li>\n  </ul>\n  <div class=\"display\" id=\"display\">✧ 点击选择 ✧</div>\n</div>\n<script>\nlet last = null;\nfunction pick(el, txt) {\n  last?.classList.remove('selected');\n  el.classList.add('selected');\n  last = el;\n  const d = document.getElementById('display');\n  d.innerText = txt;\n  d.classList.add('active');\n  try {\n    const ta = window.parent.document.querySelector('#send_textarea');\n    if (!ta) return;\n    ta.value = txt;\n    ta.dispatchEvent(new Event('input', { bubbles: true }));\n  } catch(e) {}\n}\n</script>\n</body>\n</html>\n```",
